                            dst-mac ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff

echo "Filter Configuration"

    filter 
        ip-filter 50 create
            default-action forward
            description "limit_www" 
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 30 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 80
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 40 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 8080
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        ip-filter 445 create
            default-action forward
            entry 10 create
                match protocol tcp
                    dst-port eq 445
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match protocol udp
                    dst-port eq 445
                exit 
                action
                    drop
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
        mac-filter 777 create
            default-action forward
            entry 10 create
                match frame-type 802dot3
                    src-mac 1c:75:08:67:b3:07 ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                exit 
                log 101
                action
                    forward
                exit
            exit 
            entry 20 create
                match frame-type 802dot3
                    src-mac 44:37:e6:a2:9c:c4 ff:ff:ff:ff:ff:ff
                exit 
                log 101
                action
                    forward
                exit
            exit 
        exit 
    exit
